All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
DatabaseConnection
The DatabaseConnection class is responsible for establishing a connection to the SQLite database.
GetNearby
The GetNearby class is responsible for retrieving nearby lecturers based on a given room number.
LecsRomBot
The LecsRomBot class represents a Telegram bot that allows users to search for SOC lecturer rooms.
Lecturer
The Lecturer class represents a lecturer in the SOC (School of Computing) department.
Main
The Main class is the entry point of the program.
SearchRoom
The SearchRoom class is responsible for searching the room of a lecturer in the database.
